{"id":2275,"date":"2021-12-23T17:14:57","date_gmt":"2021-12-23T16:14:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/?p=2275"},"modified":"2022-02-21T14:48:13","modified_gmt":"2022-02-21T13:48:13","slug":"cf-initiative-launched","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/2021\/12\/cf-initiative-launched\/","title":{"rendered":"Call for Projects: Crowdfunding Initiative Launched!"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<p>We are excited and proud to announce the launch of the OPERAS Crowdfunding Initiative \u2013 a special Christmas surprise for the Social Sciences and Humanities (SSH) community!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"the-operas-channel-on-the-wemakeit-platform\">The OPERAS Channel on the wemakeit platform<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To promote the use of crowdfunding in its community, the OPERAS Research Infrastructure is launching a dedicated channel on the crowdfunding platform <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wemakeit.com<\/a>: the <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS Channel<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We invite researchers from all Social Sciences and Humanities disciplines to run their crowdfunding campaign with the <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS channel<\/a>, get tips from the wemakeit experts to boost their campaign and benefit from the support of the OPERAS community.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/operas-channel.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2276\" width=\"185\" height=\"185\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/operas-channel.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/operas-channel-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/operas-channel-270x270.png 270w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/operas-channel-230x230.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 185px) 100vw, 185px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you are an early career researcher in a university or other research institution, an independent researcher, or an established scholar looking to start a new line of research, the wemakeit platform is for you. No matter if you need funds to publish critical editions, to organise scientific exhibitions, to launch surveys and studies with local or global impact, the <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS channel<\/a> is the way to go!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The first researchers that will launch their project campaign in early 2022 will, as a bonus, receive extra support by an external communication agency, funded by the French Ministry for Education, Research and Innovation!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can find the conditions for participation and more information in the FAQ on the <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS channel web page<\/a>. If you have further questions, please send us an email at <a href=\"mailto:operas@wemakeit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">operas@wemakeit.com<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"introduction-workshop-on-13-january\">Introduction workshop on 13 January<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you curious about what crowdfunding can do for you and for the Social Sciences and Humanities? Just one hint: it is not just about money.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you consider starting a project campaign with us, but do not know where to start, we offer a 1-hour introduction workshop on <strong>Thursday, 13 January 2022 at 17:00 CET<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The science crowdfunding experts from wemakeit will provide you with tips and tools to understand what crowdfunding is, how it can be applied to science, and how to launch your own campaign on the <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS channel<\/a> of wemakeit to collect financial support from the crowd, but also communicate your research in the most exciting format. The presentation will be followed by 30 minutes of Q&amp;A \u2013 we want to make sure you have all the information you need to get started with your project.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Register <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/e\/1FAIpQLScwr21t7B3xBdKXztk-L8v_dzAFBIHDD7YyQHWtgZ-ZWvIl4Q\/viewform?usp=sf_link\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> for free:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/e\/1FAIpQLScwr21t7B3xBdKXztk-L8v_dzAFBIHDD7YyQHWtgZ-ZWvIl4Q\/viewform?usp=sf_link\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1592\" width=\"122\" height=\"122\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b-270x270.png 270w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b-230x230.png 230w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noun_click_220443b.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 122px) 100vw, 122px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:2px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>You will be sent a Zoom-Link a few days prior to the event.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"why-a-collaboration-of-operas-and-wemakeit\">Why a collaboration of OPERAS and wemakeit?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.operas-eu.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS<\/a> is the Research Infrastructure supporting open scholarly communication in the Social Sciences and Humanities (SSH) in the European Research Area. The aim of OPERAS is to make Open Science a reality for research in the SSH and achieve a scholarly communication system where knowledge produced in the SSH benefits researchers, academics, students and more generally the whole society across Europe and worldwide, without barriers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>OPERAS is creating a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.operas-eu.org\/services\/\">portfo<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.operas-eu.org\/services\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">l<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.operas-eu.org\/services\/\">io<\/a> of different scholarly communication services at European level, addressing the specific needs of the research community. One of these services is the discovery platform <a href=\"http:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">GoTriple<\/a>, developed by us, the TRIPLE project (2019\u20132023). It is through the TRIPLE project that <a href=\"https:\/\/www.operas-eu.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wemakeit<\/a> collaborate.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Google-Form-image-CF-Workshop-1024x256.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2277\" width=\"879\" height=\"220\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Google-Form-image-CF-Workshop-1024x256.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Google-Form-image-CF-Workshop-300x75.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Google-Form-image-CF-Workshop-768x192.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Google-Form-image-CF-Workshop-1536x384.png 1536w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Google-Form-image-CF-Workshop.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 879px) 100vw, 879px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to its core discovery function, the GoTriple platform integrates a range of other innovative services and tools, including a crowdfunding platform. Both platforms, GoTriple and the <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS channel<\/a> from wemakeit, are interconnected to provide an ideal environment for SSH researchers and their projects.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wemakeit<\/a> was founded in Switzerland in 2012 and is now one of the largest crowdfunding platforms in Europe, with a total of over 66 million Euro of backings, more than 5,500 successful projects and almost 500,000 community members.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>wemakeit collaborates with a range of different partners, among them media partners, foundations, organisations and companies. OPERAS is one of them, and the <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OPERAS channel<\/a> is one of currently <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/channels\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">13 active channels and initiatives<\/a> of wemakeit that back and support projects.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"are-you-in\">Are you in?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Excited to crowdfund your research project and be supported by the OPERAS community? We can\u2019t wait to learn more about your project idea!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All necessary information and the conditions of participation are available here: <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/operas<\/a>. You can also contact us by email at <a href=\"mailto:operas@wemakeit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">operas@wemakeit.com<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can find general information on starting a project on the wemakeit platform here: <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/start-a-project\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/start-a-project<\/a> and guidelines here: <a href=\"https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/guidelines\">https:\/\/wemakeit.com\/pages\/guidelines<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Further resources on crowdfunding (i.e. links to articles, papers, presentations) are here: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/crowdfunding-resources\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/crowdfunding-resources<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We are excited and proud to announce the launch of the OPERAS Crowdfunding Initiative \u2013 a special Christmas surprise for the Social Sciences and Humanities (SSH) community! The OPERAS Channel on the wemakeit platform To promote the use of crowdfunding<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":2288,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[23,22,25],"tags":[10],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2275"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2275"}],"version-history":[{"count":16,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2275\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2395,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2275\/revisions\/2395"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2288"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2275"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2275"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2275"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}